# Workspace session notes (per-session, not versioned)
**/.session-notes

# Per-project learning data (generated at runtime)
.claude/learning/
.claude/rules/learned-instincts.md

# Per-operator local identity + runtime telemetry (operator-local; NEVER committed/synced)
# .claude/operator-id contains GPG verified_id fingerprint per multi-operator-coordination.md;
# .claude/logs/ carries telemetry (coc-telemetry-autocommit.log etc.) per knowledge-convergence.md
.claude/operator-id
.claude/logs/

# Operator-local deployment-value siblings (same disclosure class as .claude/operator-id).
# Convention: <file>.operator.local.<ext> + <file>.local.<ext> hold deployment-specific
# values (org slugs, runner hostnames, resolver path overrides). The paired
# <file>.local.example.<ext> / <file>.operator.local.example.<ext> SCHEMAS stay tracked
# — they are the operator-facing templates. Narrow per-dir patterns chosen so audit
# fixtures under .claude/audit-fixtures/**/*.operator.local.* (intended-tracked) are
# NOT over-ignored.
.claude/rules/*.operator.local.md
.claude/bin/*.local.json

# CC worktree-isolation per-operator session state (one subdir per agent)
.claude/worktrees/

# Internal docs (not for distribution)
/docs/01-kailash-vibe-cc-internals/

# Generated script outputs (sdk-users examples)
**/scripts/data/
**/scripts/outputs/
**/scripts/*.log
